Type: UI/UX

Title: Inconsistent objective marker behavior during mission tracking

Environment:

Platform: PC / Console
Mode: Main Story Missions

Steps to Reproduce:

Start a mission with multiple objectives
Switch between objectives rapidly
Track markers on HUD/map

Expected Result:
Objective markers update consistently and accurately reflect current target

Actual Result:
Markers lag, disappear temporarily, or point to incorrect locations

Severity: Medium

Impact:
Causes confusion and disrupts mission flow

Notes:
More frequent in complex missions with multiple triggers
